# API Pattern

## Structure

- Abstract interface: `auth_api.dart`
- Implementation: `auth_api_impl.dart`
- Endpoints in `data/data_sources/remote/constants/network_constants.dart`
- Map `DioException` → `ApiException`
- Return domain entities, not raw maps

## Registration

Register in `data/di/module/network_module/network_module.dart`:

```dart
getIt.registerLazySingleton<AuthApi>(
  () => AuthApiImpl(getIt<DioClient>()),
);
```
